title: Colombia Unemployed Persons
description: The number of unemployed persons in Colombia increased to 2696.32 Thousand in September of 2022 from 2636 Thousand in August of 2022. Unemployed Persons in Colombia averaged 2494.42 Thousand from 2001 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 4655.54 Thousand in May of 2020 and a record low of 1746.05 Thousand in November of 2015. In Colombia, unemployed persons are individuals who are without a job and actively seeking to work. This page provides - Colombia Unemployed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Dane, Colombia
